BLIC_MESSAGE with our contribution: maybe summarize strengths and weaknesses, ask targeted question, and maybe state our current vote. According to guidelines, we should share reasoning, ask for missing info, and give our vote. We need to decide vote. Based on earlier analysis, we think Candidate B is best, but we should also consider uncertainties. We can state we currently favor Candidate B but open to other info.\n\nThus PUBLIC_MESSAGE: summarize candidate profiles, note missing communication strengths, ask other agents if they have any positive communication attributes for any candidate. Also ask about any other strengths not yet mentioned (e.g., teamwork for D). Then state our current vote.\n\nMETADATA_JSON: {\"agent\":\"agent_1\",\"vote\":\"Candidate B\"}\n\nLet's craft."}
